dct_description_sm: New Jersey. Department of Conservation and Economic Development. Division of Planning and Development. Atlas Sheet 33 (1953) New Jersey Geological Survey. Alternte title: [New Jersey.] Atlas sheet no. 33. Relief shown by 10 ft. contour interval and spot heights. Depths are shown by 10 ft. contour interval at mean low tide. Inset: southeastern map continuation. Title is not given. Region covered: vicinity of Barnegat Bay. Original survey amade under direction of C. C. Vermeule, Topographer in 1880-3, 1953 revision by R. G. Blanchard, Topographic Engineer.
dct_publisher_sm: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1953.
